{"tid":1797031,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好洩氣 要繼續和你shop","createTime":"2019-12-25T05:44:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-25T10:20:50.000Z","uid":1988,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c8c60f7220df738686c34f3cee2ddcc00eef9d95","tid":1797031,"uid":1988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T05:44:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n手足唔係condom<br />\n我地要代唔可以行出黎嘅手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n戰鬥落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f772899d140ae4694d4275d4ae110c13d622b06d","tid":1797031,"uid":1988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T05:46:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8717449846c240e6b93c3d5abd6cf6e4ea79d709","tid":1797031,"uid":334720,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T05:47:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">1) 落閘就目標已達成, 可以轉場。商場落閘基本上都係因為D狗入撚哂黎, 咁達成目標 無需要再屌狗同戀戰<br />\n<br />\n2) 街坊被捕個時麻煩街坊咪撚係度嘈, 琴日已經有幾次係因為街坊太嘈, 個街坊大聲叫都無人聽到佢講乜, 咁樣同害9自己友無分別。一陣無名無姓無資料, 係咪想人地被消失??<br />\n<br />\n3) 回馬槍，D狗走個時唔撚好再上前。尤其是商場入面，例如琴日ＹＯＨＯ已經比人回馬槍左起碼3-4次。每次都捉撚左2-3個。屌狗還屌狗, 你地係後面屌就爽, 企前面既街坊就中伏。唔好再做豬隊友<br />\n<br />\n4) 12點好撤。目的係經濟攬炒。請問留到咁夜對政權既傷害係邊度? 個撚個都返鳩哂屋企訓教, 車又少。同玩平原戰 自殺有咩分別? 大家要記住個目標係乜野。街上又無其他路人幫你地cover, 過左12點又無車走。好似琴日MK咁, D人又話走唔撚到比狗包圍住。咁唔該你地今日咪撚再要呀寶出動</span>"},{"pid":"89769cb3824551637ed8183de995dd96481defa5","tid":1797031,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"87174